<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>lyh lsh rạfḍ</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 qrạr- lyh lsh rạfḍ ḥby lyk
 lyh lsh rạfḍ bry lyk
 lyh lsh rạfḍ fdạỷy w nʿmty ạlly tkẖlṣk
 lyh lsh rạfḍ dʿwty
 lyh lsh rạfḍ rḥmty
 lyh ạ̹nt qạbl mwt ạ̉kyd w ạ̹ydy lyk rạḥ tnqdẖk
 1-
 ạ̹sẖtqt lyk jwạk ạ̉kyd ḥnyn lbytk ạlmwjwd jwạyạ
 ạ̉nạ ḥbytk jyt w fdytk qạʿd bʿyd mstny ạ̹yh ?
 2- ạ̹rjʿly tạny mn ʿạlm fạny hynthy ftḥ ʿynyk ạ̉nạ mstnyk fy rjwʿk ʿyd dạ mkạnk hnạ tskn fy gẖny̱ msẖ kạlʿbyd</lyrics>
